def plot1(amplitude, color):
    fig = figure()
    x = linspace(0, 10, 1000)
    grid(True)
    xlim(0, 10)
    ylim(-1.1, 1.1)
    plot(x, amplitude * np.sin(x), color=color,
            lw=5, alpha=0.4)
    
    return fig
